title: "Sentry PM-CLI-2K: schema migration input error crosses CLI boundary as high TypeError"
description: Expected invalid schema-migration input currently reaches the public SDK requiredText guard and is captured as a handled high-severity TypeError. Add a typed CLI usage boundary while preserving strict SDK validation so expected user errors remain actionable without blocking the release reliability gate.
