resolution: "Added CLI preflight validation for schema migration source, target, and stable migration id; preserved strict SDK validation and resolved PM-CLI-2K after live verification."
expected_result: Incomplete schema migration CLI input returns a typed usage error and does not create a high-severity Sentry issue.
actual_result: CLI returns schema_migration_input_required with exit 2 and compact recovery; SDK remains strict; live Sentry gate reports zero critical/high issues.
